## Commit Guidelines

### Commit Message Format
```
[type]: [agent] brief description

Examples:
feat: [backend] implement offline order creation
fix: [security] resolve XSS vulnerability in search
test: [testing] add comprehensive order tests
docs: [devops] update Docker configuration
```

### Branch Strategy
- `main`: Production-ready code
- `develop`: Integration branch
- `phase1-{task}`: Phase 1 feature branches
- `phase2-{task}`: Phase 2 feature branches

